- app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/PostController.php

Explanation:
- The route setup in routes/api.php maps DELETE requests to /v1/posts/{post} to App\Http\Controllers\Api\V1\PostController@destroy.
- The PostController class implementing the destroy method is located at app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/PostController.php.
- The destroy method in this file handles the delete action by:
  - authorizing the delete operation on the given Post,
  - deleting the post, and
  - returning a 204 No Content response.
- Therefore, this single file contains the implementation of App\Http\Controllers\Api\V1\PostController@destroy.
